sequenceDiagram
    participant SaaS as SaaS Platform<br/>(Account A)
    participant KMS as KMS<br/>(Account A)
    participant Customer as Customer Role<br/>(Account B)
    participant S3 as S3 Bucket<br/>(Account A)

    Note over SaaS,Customer: Onboarding: Create Grant
    SaaS->>KMS: CreateGrant(keyId, grantee=CustomerRole, ops=[Decrypt])
    KMS-->>SaaS: GrantToken + GrantId
    Note over KMS: Grant is EVENTUALLY CONSISTENT<br/>(up to 5 min to propagate)

    Note over Customer,S3: Immediate Use: Decrypt via Grant Token
    Customer->>S3: GetObject (encrypted with CMK)
    S3-->>Customer: Encrypted object + encrypted data key
    Customer->>KMS: Decrypt(encryptedDataKey, grantTokens=[token],<br/>encryptionContext={"tenant":"customer-123"})
    KMS-->>Customer: Plaintext data key
    Note over Customer: Decrypt object locally

    Note over Customer,S3: After ~5 min: No Token Needed
    Customer->>KMS: Decrypt(encryptedDataKey,<br/>encryptionContext={"tenant":"customer-123"})
    KMS-->>Customer: Plaintext data key

    Note over SaaS,Customer: Offboarding: Revoke Grant
    SaaS->>KMS: RevokeGrant(keyId, grantId)
    KMS-->>SaaS: Success
    Customer->>KMS: Decrypt(encryptedDataKey)
    KMS--xCustomer: AccessDenied
